  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e616f8811977561a4ecbfc19e57f32da.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e616f8811977561a4ecbfc19e57f32da.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e616f8811977561a4ecbfc19e57f32da.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sunshower is a colorful, casual arcade action game that follows a robot's survival in a rain storm!</strong> Use the plant installed on your head to reach for the sky as you achieve high scores and stop the rain from washing away the world. Enjoy a transforming, traditionally illustrated watercolor background and fun new music that appear as you gain more points. And, as you play more, find out what the robot you're controlling, Hinata, thinks of your time playing together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/45a1a256fe0a10f2b124f292ce094924.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/45a1a256fe0a10f2b124f292ce094924.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/45a1a256fe0a10f2b124f292ce094924.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect, combine, and chain power-ups to stop the rainfall!</strong> Gain more strength to carry more drops, increase your speed, or use an umbrella to deflect one drop. Every playthrough is unique!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/de0ceddf4197683ee51b52f0198778e0.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/de0ceddf4197683ee51b52f0198778e0.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/de0ceddf4197683ee51b52f0198778e0.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock 8 different customization options and an alternate, more challenging single player mode!</strong> Compete in online global leaderboards for every mode and try collecting 12 Steam achievements to show off your Sunshower skills. You can even contribute to a global drop counter and join the world to find out how many raindrops we can collect together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/f72e997bb0838adb59379d3d734a7709.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/f72e997bb0838adb59379d3d734a7709.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/f72e997bb0838adb59379d3d734a7709.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Try local co-op to reach for your highest score with a friend or compete to see who comes out on top!</strong> If you don't have an extra controller, you can use two halves of the same keyboard instead. Play together online using Steam Remote Play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e9a023903a66c6d3c43be51253736c8a.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e9a023903a66c6d3c43be51253736c8a.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e9a023903a66c6d3c43be51253736c8a.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e616f8811977561a4ecbfc19e57f32da.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e616f8811977561a4ecbfc19e57f32da.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e616f8811977561a4ecbfc19e57f32da.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sunshower is a colorful, casual arcade action game that follows a robot's survival in a rain storm!</strong> Use the plant installed on your head to reach for the sky as you achieve high scores and stop the rain from washing away the world. Enjoy a transforming, traditionally illustrated watercolor background and fun new music that appear as you gain more points. And, as you play more, find out what the robot you're controlling, Hinata, thinks of your time playing together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/45a1a256fe0a10f2b124f292ce094924.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/45a1a256fe0a10f2b124f292ce094924.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/45a1a256fe0a10f2b124f292ce094924.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect, combine, and chain power-ups to stop the rainfall!</strong> Gain more strength to carry more drops, increase your speed, or use an umbrella to deflect one drop. Every playthrough is unique!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/de0ceddf4197683ee51b52f0198778e0.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/de0ceddf4197683ee51b52f0198778e0.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/de0ceddf4197683ee51b52f0198778e0.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock 8 different customization options and an alternate, more challenging single player mode!</strong> Compete in online global leaderboards for every mode and try collecting 12 Steam achievements to show off your Sunshower skills. You can even contribute to a global drop counter and join the world to find out how many raindrops we can collect together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/f72e997bb0838adb59379d3d734a7709.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/f72e997bb0838adb59379d3d734a7709.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/f72e997bb0838adb59379d3d734a7709.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Try local co-op to reach for your highest score with a friend or compete to see who comes out on top!</strong> If you don't have an extra controller, you can use two halves of the same keyboard instead. Play together online using Steam Remote Play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e9a023903a66c6d3c43be51253736c8a.poster.avif?t=1758309630\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e9a023903a66c6d3c43be51253736c8a.webm?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942850/extras/e9a023903a66c6d3c43be51253736c8a.mp4?t=1758309630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
